                           CORPS Text Server 0.3.0
                           =======================

This package contains a simple text server for CORPS - The CORBA
Roleplaying System. This server simply echos text of all connected
clients to all other clients.

Requirements
------------

The latest version of corps-core and its dependencies.

Installing
----------

See the file INSTALL for information about compiling and installing the
package.

